		<div class="comment-content-wrap">

			<div class="comment-content" itemprop="commentText">
				<p>I, too, love the image quality of &#8220;deep&#8221; black levels of plasma sets. I also enjoy the fast refresh rates (much less fast action &#8220;smudging&#8221; than LCD&#8217;s or LED&#8217;s, to my eyes) and the wide viewing angles of plasma sets. It seems to me that 50&#8243; plasma sets, for the buyer, are the financial &#8220;sweet spot&#8221; in HDTV sets at the present time; I&#8217;m sorry they&#8217;re going away.</p>
